'''奥利弗镇区'''是[[美国|美国]][[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[亚当斯县_(俄亥俄州)|亚当斯县]]的一个镇区，[[2010年美国人口普查|2010年美国人口普查]]时有1319人居住在该镇区。<ref name="Census 2010">{{cite web| url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/DEC/10_DP/G001/0600000US3900128196| title=Geographic Identifiers: 2010 Demographic Profile Data (G001): Franklin township, Adams County, Ohio| publisher=U.S. Census Bureau, American Factfinder| accessdate=July 5, 2013}}</ref>

全州仅有此一个奥利弗镇区。<ref>{{Cite web| title = Detailed map of Ohio| work = | publisher = [[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]]| year = 2000| url = http://www2.census.gov/geo/maps/general_ref/cousub_outline/cen2k_pgsz/oh_cosub.pdf| format = PDF| accessdate = 2007-02-16| archive-date = 2007-03-16| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070316053708/http://www2.census.gov/geo/maps/general_ref/cousub_outline/cen2k_pgsz/oh_cosub.pdf| dead-url = no}}</ref>

==地理==
奥利弗镇区位于亚当斯县中部，与以下镇区接壤：
*[[斯科特镇区_(俄亥俄州亚当斯县)|斯科特镇区]] - 北
*[[梅格斯镇区_(俄亥俄州亚当斯县)|梅格斯镇区]] - 东
*[[蒂芬镇区_(俄亥俄州亚当斯县)|蒂芬镇区]] - 南
*[[韦恩镇区_(俄亥俄州亚当斯县)|韦恩镇区]] - 西

==历史==
奥利弗镇区建于1853，命名源自县行政长官约翰·奥利弗<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=8HwUAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA453#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=A History of Adams County, Ohio: From Its Earliest Settlement to the Present Time | publisher=E B. Stivers | author=Evans, Nelson Wiley | year=1900 | pages=453 | access-date=2015-09-13 | archive-date=2017-12-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171217030319/https://books.google.com/books?id=8HwUAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA453#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==政府==
镇区有3人组成的理事会管理。理事会理事选举在奇数年11月举行，并在来年1月1日开始四年任期。两名理事的选举在总统选举后一年举行，另一名的选举在总统选举前一年举行。镇区财务官亦由选举产生<ref>[http://codes.ohio.gov/orc/503.24 §503.24] {{Wayback|url=http://codes.ohio.gov/orc/503.24 |date=20090721175921 }}, [http://codes.ohio.gov/orc/505.01 §505.01] {{Wayback|url=http://codes.ohio.gov/orc/505.01 |date=20081231032851 }}, and [http://codes.ohio.gov/orc/507.01 §507.01] {{Wayback|url=http://codes.ohio.gov/orc/507.01 |date=20090721175216 }} of the [[Ohio_Revised_Code|Ohio Revised Code]]. Accessed 4/30/2009.</ref>，与一名镇区理事选举同时举行，不过在来年4月1日才开始四年任期。若财务官或理事职位有空缺，将由剩余理事填补。

